Author: Dalos_
Text: I was forced to leave college my second semester there to go inpatient. It’s not worth struggling over in college because it’ll just end up being an expensive mess. If you have the choice and control now to receive help, please, please reach out.

Author: glokash
Text: If your university provides you with good health insurance, I’d say reach out for help now and get some support lined up just in case.   It’s hard to graduate when you can’t think due to the eating disorder.
